OL,3,CNew council boss to receive #192,000
OL,4,Csalary
OL,6,FThe new chief executive of Bristol
OL,7,FCity Council will be on a #192,000
OL,8,Fsalary, which will rise each year.
OL,10,FThe local authority had refused to
OL,11,Fdisclose the amount Nick Hibberd would
OL,12,Fbe paid when he begins in January,
OL,13,Fdespite it being a legal requirement
OL,14,Ffor figures to be published in its
OL,15,Fannual statement of accounts.
OL,17,FCllr Kelvin Blake (Labour, Hillfields)
OL,18,Fhas now successfully challenged the
OL,19,Fdecision to withhold the figures.
