OL,3,CNew council boss to receive #192,000
OL,4,Csalary
OL,6,FIn a written question to member forum
OL,7,Fon Tuesday, 12 November, he said:
OL,8,F"It's important for the public to know
OL,9,Fhow taxpayer money is spent.
OL,11,F"Why have you not released the newly
OL,12,Fappointed chief executive's salary?
OL,14,F"Please could you inform us of what
OL,15,Fthe salary is?"
OL,17,FCouncil leader Cllr Tony Dyer (Green,
OL,18,FSouthville) replied: "We don't usually
OL,19,Fcomment on individual salary
OL,20,Finformation as it is personal data.
