OL,3,CNew council boss to receive #192,000
OL,4,Csalary
OL,6,F"Salary bands are published in the pay
OL,7,Fpolicy statement on the council
OL,8,Fwebsite and the remuneration of senior
OL,9,Fofficers is also published on the
OL,10,Fwebsite as part of our annual
OL,11,Fstatement of accounts, which is a
OL,12,Fstatutory requirement.
OL,14,F"However, I do have the permission of
OL,15,Four newly appointed chief executive to
OL,16,Frelease his salary information.
