OL,3,CNew council boss to receive #192,000
OL,4,Csalary
OL,6,F"The selection committee appointed him
OL,7,Fat the top of the pay band, which,
OL,8,Ftaking into account the recent
OL,9,Fnational pay award for local authority
OL,10,Fchief executives, is an annual salary
OL,11,Fof #191,843."
OL,13,FThat equates to #3,689.29 a week, or
OL,14,F#737.86 daily, before tax.
OL,16,FCllr Dyer said the role was graded
OL,17,Findependently using an approved method
OL,18,Fand comparing it with similar
OL,19,Fpositions elsewhere.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@MO]
