OL,6,FHe said Mr Hibberd's salary would rise
OL,7,Feach year in line with national Joint
OL,8,FNegotiating Committee pay awards for
OL,9,Fsenior council officers.
OL,11,FAt the meeting, Cllr Blake asked:
OL,12,F"Would you agree with me that
OL,13,Ftransparency around public spending is
OL,14,Fvital?
OL,26,@tD@AOU
