OL,3,CNew council boss to receive #192,000
OL,4,Csalary
OL,6,F"I understand the sensitivities around
OL,7,Fsalaries, however, it's really
OL,8,Fimportant to maintain confidence from
OL,9,Fthe public about how we spend public
OL,10,Fmoney and I wondered whether Tony
OL,11,Fwould wholeheartedly agree with those
OL,12,Fsentiments?"
OL,14,FCllr Dyer replied: "I agree it's
OL,15,Fvitally important that we are very
OL,16,Fcareful with how we spend public money.
OL,18,F"It's also important that we respect
OL,19,Findividual privacy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]vD@TOUzD@AOU
