OL,3,CNew council boss to receive #192,000
OL,4,Csalary
OL,6,F"What I can say in the interests of
OL,7,Fsome additional information is that
OL,8,Famong the core cities, Bristol has the
OL,9,Flowest salary paid to its chief
OL,10,Fexecutive."
OL,12,FFull council unanimously approved the
OL,13,Fnew top boss's appointment in October.
OL,15,FMr Hibberd, who will replace interim
OL,16,Fchief exec Paul Martin on 6 January,
OL,17,Fhas more than 25 years' experience at
OL,18,Fthe top level of local government and
OL,19,Fmost recently worked for London
OL,20,FBorough of Croydon's corporate
OL,21,Fmanagement team.
